WEBVTT

28:25.899 --> 28:27.316
-their father is a criminal?
-Hey!

28:27.608 --> 28:28.858
They'd never think that way.

28:29.483 --> 28:31.858
I'm starting to think that way myself.
So why wouldn't they?

28:31.899 --> 28:33.566
You don't have to think
like that anymore.

28:33.608 --> 28:34.608
It's all over, isn't it?
